metadata.name: Listen To The Forest
metadata.description:
Southeast Asian rainforests are believed to be the oldest and some of the most biologically diverse forests in the world. However, human activities have severely impacted the ecosystem of the rainforest, placing many species at risk of extinction.

'Listen To The Forest' is a tribute to the world’s rainforests, the spectacular wildlife and biodiversity they nurture, the role they play for the environment and human evolution.

‘Listen To The Forest' is an Open Edition, minted on a ERC-1155 smart contract and now claimable through Manifold Studio.

License: Primary NFT holder is free to use for private display and in groups including virtual galleries. Provides no rights for commercial use, merchandise, distribution, or derivative works. Copyright remains with creator.
